plot1 <- simple.sf %>% ggplot() + geom_sf(shape=20) +
theme_grey() +
  theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.x=element_blank())
plot2 <- arransubsect %>%
  ggplot() +
  geom_sf() +
  theme_grey() +
  theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.x=element_blank()) +
  geom_sf(data=simple.sf, shape=20)
plot3 <- arran2016 %>%

  theme_grey() +
  theme(legend.position="none") +
  theme(axis.text.x=element_blank(),
        axis.ticks.x=element_blank()) +
  geom_sf(data=simple.sf, shape=20)

plot5 <- S01004372 %>%
